AirTran's all-new Boeing 717
The people of AirTran Airways have brought some sizeable
improvements to low-fare flying, such as assigned seating, an affordable
Business Class, and our A-Plus Rewards frequent flier program.
But we think now we may have really outdone ourselves.
On September 24, 1999, AirTran became the first airline in
the world to take delivery of the all-new Boeing 717. It's the quietest,
